API reference:​ Use https://coinmarketcap.com/api/ for all api related documentation.

A table showing coins with columns of current price and marketcap.
Upon clicking on any row, its Price Chart View​, should open.
It should have price of coin against time, for last 24 hrs.
Frontend Technologies allowed - Angular for dynamism and SPA and any technologies /framework allowed for frontend design. Use any library/technology to draw and charts. Here are some important points -

You are free to allowed to do design changes - layout, colors, font, icon, animations etc. Extra points will be given for creativity.
You may use bootstrap and related components for layout design.
Your web pages must be fully responsive.
